{"tid":964984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哈薩克人擺習近平肖像 霸氣狂轟3槍","createTime":"2019-01-01T16:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T15:58:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":461,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ef402107187b90e766e982359bdd2f41a25f49","tid":964984,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpOHy72b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpOHy72b.jpg&h=8ecfb578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國當局在新疆濫抓維吾爾族、哈薩克族民眾，不少當地人對於中國領導人習近平心生不滿，有逃出中國、進入哈薩克國境的民眾為求洩恨，在空曠的地上擺放習近平肖像，對著它狂轟3槍，網友對此指出「比潑墨還猛」、「超霸氣」。<br />\n<br />\n一名哈薩克族民眾12月28日在臉書上貼出開槍影片，從中可見到他的友人穿著深藍色長袖上衣與灰色長褲，在空曠的哈薩克國境空地，拿著獵槍朝著地上的習近平肖像連轟3槍，3發子彈全部命中習肖像的右臉頰部位，開完槍後，肖像也被風吹走。<br />\n<br />\n貼出影片的哈薩克族民眾，在臉書張貼了許多哈薩克族人資訊，同時關注中國官方對於同胞的迫害行為，他們透過臉書傳遞訊息，向逃出中國的同胞告知在中國境內的親友下落如何；在開槍影片當中，PO文民眾將習近平形容成「中國恐怖份子（Chinese Terrorist）」。<br />\n<br />\n網友們看見中國領導人習近平成為哈薩克族民眾的槍靶子，均感到比先前發生的上海潑墨事件更為勁爆，紛紛留言指出「大快人心」、「敬你是條漢子」、「下次使用AK47」、「他就像條狗」、「希特勒還比習近平要好點呢」、「老百姓只知道追求事實！不會活在中國共匪的謊言之下」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=uUQAYBwTlho&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuUQAYBwTlho%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=WG6PQImSObb%2BJCOg9v3r5ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c0555204\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=uUQAYBwTlho&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2659173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2659173&d=WG6PQImSObb%2BJCOg9v3r5ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d518cc1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2659173&h=f4d01c70\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2659173</a>"},{"pid":"7dade42468e26f0725904f470899d2526b764118","tid":964984,"uid":143306,"like":287,"dislike":16,"score":271,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"肖像？？？<br />\n轟真人就話你威"},{"pid":"285fe98393d4fe684c1c3b334bbec0c3754e67b9","tid":964984,"uid":188,"like":166,"dislike":4,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"觀看次數：2 次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e46627c3f6bb08cdc53d5ec10fea0003f4787c8","tid":964984,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7e3e84cb3df44f6375072e5e3dbbd6a148ac89","tid":964984,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"以為佢有勇氣出鏡"},{"pid":"b289487182df92981e6e65c8e0aece8275cf773b","tid":964984,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2202d9deaeeeb5f602fed886cf4384de4524d0e2","tid":964984,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ec7e3e84cb3df44f6375072e5e3dbbd6a148ac89","tid":964984,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"以為佢有勇氣出鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"有洗頭艇"},{"pid":"790ce3bb74d9ba290af688e6ed7ea4d661316dfb","tid":964984,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T00:56:39.000Z","msg":"霸氣到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1105a569d915daafe49e0e4f148694453211c80","tid":964984,"uid":76776,"like":84,"dislike":5,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:05:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b71a68652d848a66c3eee11effb8628