株待兔方法通宵監視，至昨晨8時拘捕手持原子筆，懷疑企圖再在梯間犯案姓林（46歲）男住客。本月7日至本周三，錦葵閣四樓、五樓、八至九樓梯間牆壁，先後三度出現「習近平去死」字句。"},{"pid":"cacb0cd31a50158854c5fc4b0d9ae58f3e540a2c","tid":964984,"uid":13149,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"2c73b1dd4a940c444ded0421e36e6abd9458bd72","tid":964984,"uid":20867,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"Meanwhile in HKSARS ...<br />\n<br />\n「習近平去死」塗鴉　警通宵監視拉人 <br />\n【本報訊】馬鞍山錦豐苑三現「習近平去死」字句案件，警方出動重案組調查，即時拉人。前晚第三度案發後，沙田警區重案組探員進駐事發的錦葵閣，採消極的守株待兔方法通宵監視，至昨晨8時拘捕手持原子筆，懷疑企圖再在梯間犯案姓林（46歲）男住客。本月7日至本周三，錦葵閣四樓、五樓、八至九樓梯間牆壁，先後三度出現「習近平去死」字句。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"咁都要重案組？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdfbca88618edef82fa30d75d5d1668c229ce8e","tid":964984,"uid":51625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c8c6d4a4fe3e5df114cb3f68804a8cd8d4bb66a3","tid":964984,"uid":55913,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:17:36.000Z","msg":"聖上 而家應該揮軍西進<br />\n委任成龍為大將軍 帶3萬騎兵<br />\n吳京為副將 帶2萬精兵<br />\n剷平哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"再命香港太守林鄭氏組編十萬香港新軍以作後援。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81935d82ecc147a7e7689f15a9ff72ed9c8d6056","tid":964984,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"8136ac617c6ed9d606fc9c5bada74cc2eb6a040b","tid":964984,"uid":61882,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static1.fjcdn.com/thumbnails/comments/Kazakhstan+greatest+country+in+the+world+all+other+countrys+are+_3f99473d99133ed1a26a3ceca306aec8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.fjcdn.com%2Fthumbnails%2Fcomments%2FKazakhstan%2Bgreatest%2Bcountry%2Bin%2Bthe%2Bworld%2Ball%2Bother%2Bcountrys%2Bare%2B_3f99473d99133ed1a26a3ceca306aec8.jpg&h=0ca742df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKazakhstan gre